Helen Monks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Monks 0 Helen Monks is an English actress and writer, known for her roles in Raised by Wolves, Upstart Crow, The Archers, Holby City, The Last Kingdom, and Genius.In 2015, Monks was a runner up in the Funny Women Awards.Monks co-founded theatre company Lung in 2012.She was the original Pip Archer on The Archers. Monks is represented by actor's agents Conway van Gelder Grant.
